Source: Slang Today
Author: PARTRIDGE
Vol / Page: 287
Edition:
Quote: In London, for preference; there I can have a mag to a tabby, or if any of you fellows put the boot into me in any way, I'll parade sick and join Colonel Peerless's Light Infantry at the base.
Notes: 1935 A.E. Strong WW1 scene in Partridge Slang Today 287

